[NewMapBriefings]
;//DM-Morbias//
MorbiasDesc=The Morbias Station is a transport hub that focuses all traffic passing through Taryd's jumpgates.  The Station offers a terrestrial shuttle, storage facilities (with quarantine services for live cargo), and a social center where guests can meet incoming visitors or hold private meetings in a neutral setting.
;//CTF-FacingWorlds//
FaceDesc=The Necris have forced their way into even the most revered of Izanagi landmarks.  Their corruption has spread to the Temple of Facing Worlds, and one of its towers is already showing the effects of infection and decay.
;//CTF-Searchlight//
SearchlightDesc=The lighthouse serves as a beacon to this remote island, thought to be the ancient home of the Necris Prophet.  The spiritual components of the Necris conversion are greatly misunderstood, and their power is vastly underestimated.  Those who are willing to face the impact of their conversion often come to religious centers like this one to meditate.
